<!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
     SERVER COMMANDS
════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
<h1>Server Commands After Deployment</h1>

<p>Run the following commands in order via Hostinger SSH/Terminal after uploading all files:</p>

<span class="code"># Step 1: Run pending database migrations
php artisan migrate

# Step 2: Seed staff post types (run once only)
php artisan db:seed --class=StaffPostTypeSeeder

# Step 3: Clear all caches
php artisan view:clear
php artisan route:clear
php artisan config:clear
php artisan cache:clear</span>


