  <p><strong>Issue:</strong> Classes showing "⚙️ Not Set" or incorrect Available values in Daily Admissions</p>
  <p><strong>Cause:</strong> Total Seats was never properly saved in Class Setup for this school (stored as 0 in database)</p>
</div>

<p><strong>Manual Fix Required (no code change needed):</strong></p>
<ol>
  <li>Log in as the HOI user for IMSB (VI-X) RAWAL DAM</li>
  <li>Navigate to <strong>Classes &amp; Sections</strong></li>
  <li>For each class showing the amber "⚙️ Not Set" badge, enter the correct <strong>Total Seats</strong> value</li>
  <li>Click <strong>Save</strong></li>
  <li>Navigate to <strong>Daily Admissions</strong> — Available seats will now calculate correctly as:<br>
      <strong>Available = Total Seats − Existing Enrollment</strong></li>
</ol>


